Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.74,Notes,,0,0,0,,（真的假的）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好厲害啊 小太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你要考水野的高中？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的事都傳開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧  真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太恩愛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,結婚算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,死現充
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,水野成績很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這就要靠愛的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒那麼簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,投降投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,光明沒戲唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,偏差值需要60以上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,換我的話還好說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是小太的隊友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,模擬考試的成績下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,給  安曇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你要考光明？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一志願選了市立
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……三年一班的……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  不好意思  讓您專門跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,兒子承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,考生就是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟成績差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可能考不上志願校了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你臉色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,家人應該也很擔心你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,父母反對我考那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定希望我落榜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦的時候休息下也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,調整心情也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等大家都冷靜一下  再跟父母談談如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,599)\frz14.04\fs45}畢竟聖誕  明天見見面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.04\pos(730,149)\fs45}別太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:21.87,Notes,,0,0,0,,（好可愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  等很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒獨處過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  你明明還得學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我才該道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那……那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  可以打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你社團活動的時候也許用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那輪到我打開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  織的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧？不是吧  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是完全照著書織的啊  啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看  好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎很用功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺你上課的時候都好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,學到很晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽反對我考那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想提高成績讓她刮目相看的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可是不太順利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,家人的支持很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊  最後一次比賽時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽在便當裡留了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,三年來辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時就想  原來媽媽一直看在眼裡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然後稍微哭了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,總之  只能拿結果說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,過完年馬上就是考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(802.001,70.999)\frz4.864\fs35}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(950,160)\fs35}結果出來了再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(938.667,237.333)\fs35}啊 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(1100,350)\fs35}連我也不由得緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(900,410)\fs35}啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(1010,540)\fs35}不好意思  打擾到你學習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(1002.667,624)\fs35}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(850,714.999)\fs35}我要更加努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(1096,784)\fs35}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.864\pos(1048,866.667)\fs35}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜今天出結果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.12\pos(1200,165.333)}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.12\pos(1061.333,354.667)}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.12\pos(837.333,712)}合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說  欸？合格了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.78\pos(1354.001,567.001)}恭喜你！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.78\pos(480,391.002)}合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,通宵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,學習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,關於志願……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想考光明就考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒考上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就考並行志願的市立高中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,明白沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽  前段時間被班導師叫去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,說是憑小太郎現在的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,最好放棄考光明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽說  小太郎真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓你考
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好像意見很堅決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說了你那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,總之  就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我正打算給你送上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,來  坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:57.36,INJP,,0,0,0,,母がくれたたくさんの優しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:57.36,INCN,,0,0,0,,母親為我付出的無數溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上該早點睡了  把生物鐘調回白天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都這麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,正考睡著了還有什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:11.56,INJP,,0,0,0,,愛を抱いて歩めと繰り返した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:11.56,INCN,,0,0,0,,無數次提醒我帶上愛前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,來  喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:23.90,INJP,,0,0,0,,あの時はまだ幼くて 意味など知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:23.90,INCN,,0,0,0,,那時我還年幼  絲毫不知其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:34.05,INJP,,0,0,0,,そんな私の手を握り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:34.05,INCN,,0,0,0,,母親牽著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.88,INJP,,0,0,0,,一緒に歩んできた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.88,INCN,,0,0,0,,一路走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:45.55,INJP,,0,0,0,,その優しさを時には嫌がり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:45.55,INCN,,0,0,0,,時而也會厭惡母親的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:52.21,INJP,,0,0,0,,離れた母へ素直になれず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:52.21,INCN,,0,0,0,,無法對離開身邊的母親敞開心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:59.50,INJP,,0,0,0,,ほら 足元を見てごらん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:59.50,INCN,,0,0,0,,看啊  看著你的腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,准考證帶了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:05.82,INJP,,0,0,0,,これがあなたの歩む道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:05.82,INCN,,0,0,0,,這就是你要走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,換乘站和時間寫上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要坐錯車哦  畢竟這麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:13.00,INJP,,0,0,0,,ほら 前を見てごらん
